Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.48,0:00:34.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Les línies de la mà són metxes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:36.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,la línia del cor encén el foc\Nde la deducció."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:38.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"En Heiji i jo desxifrem\Nun codi secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:40.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,un misteri que uneix Tòquio\Ni Osaka."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:42.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:45.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:47.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,kanjou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:50.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kanpeki ni lose control
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:53.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,baguru utto ushisa ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:59.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Heki eki wakatteru.\NSutansu, sutansu, sutansu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:01.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,Itsuwari ID
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:04.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,gen'in suisoku shite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:11.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,tousou hon'nou zenkai\Numaku wa waraenai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:14.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sutensu, sutensu, sutensu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:18.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Chansu tsukamasu sutansu, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:22.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Reeru no nai michi Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:28.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Dare ni mo\Ntomerarenai kono kimochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:33.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm blowing up, I'm blowing up.\NKokoro ga sawagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:37.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm blowing up, I'm blowing up.\NOwarasenaide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:40.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mirai ga mieru\NI'm gonna be your dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:44.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh! Buttobe your dynamite!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:54.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm blowing up, I'm blowing up.\NKokoro ga sawagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:58.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm blowing up, I'm blowing up.\NOwarasenaide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,Mirai ga mieru\NI'm gonna be your dynamite.
